text: Franz Kemter (21 February 1922 - 28 February 2008) was an Austrian gymnast. He competed in eight events at the 1952 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1922 births Category:2008 deaths Category:Austrian male artistic gymnasts Category:Olympic gymnasts of Austria Category:Gymnasts at the 1952 Summer Olympics Category:People from Dornbirn Category:Sportspeople from Vorarlberg
